description: Guernsey's first island-wide election will be held on 17 June, replacing the district system.
title: Guernsey election 2020: Political parties will have to register
title_page: Guernsey election 2020: Political parties will have to register - BBC News
maintext: Party names must not be "offensive" or similar to any other organisation, according to guidance issued by the States of Guernsey.
